Add to outputs.tf

output "public_ip" {
  value = azurerm_public_ip.public_ip.ip_address
}

then
terraform output public_ip

SSH
ssh azureuser@<public-ip>



Security Best Practices (DevOps Level)
instead of
source_address_prefix = "*"

use
source_address_prefix = "YOUR_PUBLIC_IP/32"

Destroy when done
terraform destroy
